Keyboard Commands:
------------------

F1 = Red Player Stats
F2 = Green Player Stats
F3 = Yellow Player Stats
F4 = Blue Player Stats
F5 = All Player's Stats
F6 = Load a Game
F7 = Save a Game
 5 = Red Players' top Screen on/off
 6 = Green Players' top Screen on/off
 7 = Yellow Players' top Screen on/off
 8 = Blue Players' top Screen on/off
 9 = Camera top Screen on/off
 0 = Mini-View on/off
-_ = Text soft/hard
=+ = Climb/Decend Shading (up/down arrows in the middle STUPID KEY!)

DEL = Left Mouse Button 
HELP= Right Mouse Button

Cursor Keys = Moves the pointer.

KEYPAD :
--------
 1 = Accend/climb/up Ladder (Zoom OUT while in space)
 2 = Backwards
 3 = Decend/down Ladder  (Zoom IN while in space)
 4 = MOVE left
 5 = NOTHING
 6 = MOVE right
 7 = Turn Left (in space 7 = ORBIT)
 8 = Forward
 9 = Turn Right (in space 9 = LAND)
ENTER = while in space it moves cursor to the ship
 - = PAUSE the game.

